"Does this new version overwrite RW 2 or is it a seperate install. If it is a new instal can I transfer my assets over .?"

You can choose to install into separate directory and install any expansions again in RW3. If you copy them over manually, make sure that you're not overwriting newer files included in RW3 with older RW2 files.

